page.title: 05The Ancient House Ipswich
page.content: The Ancient House has been a bookshop for a long time but in the last couple of years all the books have been moved to a modern building,for the Ancient House to be cleaned up. On the outside wall of the Ancient house there are engravings in the wood of different countries.One main country of today is missing from those engravings,it is America.The reason is because America had not been discovered at the time the Ancient House was built. The Ancient House used to be called the Sparrowe House and is described in books as a Tudor mansion. For years the Ancient House has been used for business and it probably go on being used for business in the future.
